::NeoGuile::
    "Oh, really?  You think I don't know what you would do?  I know that I'd 
put a means of enforcement in a copy of myself.  I assume you planted an 
explosive device in me somewhere.  No, I haven't bothered looking for it.  I 
wouldn't be able to find it myself anyway.  As for your mines, they are 
impractical.  Unless they are near the surface the explosion has no where to 
go.  Any dirt with I certain distance would be forced outward and compressed 
into a type of glass.  Thus the mines would only work if the proximity was, 
say, less than 5 or 6 feet."
